title: 99.5: Clean Up On Aisle 7 ft. Mike Majlak
description:
Today Sofia is joined by the infamous Mike Majlak! Mike is a Youtube extraordinaire, best selling author, and co-host of Impulsive with Logan Paul. Todays episode starts off hot by Sofia mispronouncing Mike’s last name even though they’ve known each other for years. Next, Sofia gets the inside scoop for the Sloots by questioning Mike about his previous relationship with Lana Rhoades and unpacking his feelings about her newborn with a mystery NBA star - which were interesting to say the least. Sloots, get your Prime from the fridge and couple names ready because Sofia and Mike just might be your new favorite content couple!
